= Configure =

cp production.sh.base production.sh
cp start.sh.base start.sh
Set the --prefix=... parameter in start.sh and production.sh if running Rubyric in a subdirectory (eg. www.example.com/rubyric).

cp config/database.yml.base config/database.yml
Set the database parameters in config/database.yml.

cp config/initializers/settings.rb.base config/initializers/settings.rb
Configure all the parameters in config/initializers/settings.rb


== Set up the database ==
rake db:schema:load
